          "anchor": "discussion",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Include this option when your activity includes left-right directions",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "in the video for the FaceTime call. The option mirrors the video along",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "the vertical axis, which makes it easy for participants to mimic an",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "instuctorâ€™s movements. Without mirroring, views move in the opposite",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "direction of the instructor, which can be jarring.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    }
  ],
